# 🚀 Rocketry-2026

## 📌 Description

This project is an **interactive rocket system visualization** that explains the internal architecture of a model rocket.
It demonstrates how avionics, payload, power systems, and control mechanisms are integrated into a real rocket design.

---

## ⚙️ Features

* Interactive rocket diagram (clickable zones)
* Detailed explanation of each rocket section
* Real-world components (STM32, MPU6050, LoRa, etc.)
* Lightweight web-based implementation (HTML, CSS, JS)
* Educational + project demonstration tool

---

## 🛠️ Tech Used

* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript
* SVG (for rocket visualization)

---

## 🚀 How to Run

```bash
git clone https://github.com/official-vnt/Rocketry-2026.git
cd Rocketry-2026
```

Open:

```bash
index.html
```

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```
Rocketry-2026/
│── index.html
│── style.css (optional)
│── script.js (optional)
│── assets/ (images if added)
```

---

## 🎯 Goal

To create a **visual + interactive explanation** of rocket subsystems for learning and demonstration purposes.

